entries.gothit1: Reverend Oni`antae! I have been hit! Help me!
entries.gothit3: You may destroy me, but you'll never destroy the Dark Veil Order!
entries.gothit4: Luck seems to be on your side, my friend. But you will not defeat me!
entries.hityou1: A small victory in a vast war against unclean beings!
entries.hityou2: May your death be quick and painless, %Nu!
entries.hityou3: We shall pay homage to your essence as it is consumed by the Heart of Dathomir!
entries.hityou5: I wish you well in the next life, infidel. The Heart of Dathomir is merciless to the unclean!
entries.entercombat1: Fear the unholy might of the Dark Veil Order!
entries.entercombat2: Reverend Oni`antae! Guide me so that we, together, may destroy this infidel!
entries.entercombat3: The cleansing will start with you, %NU!
entries.entercombat4: The sight of you disgusts me! I must cleanse you from the Heart of Dathomir!
entries.entercombat5: May your pain be quick and painless, infidel!
entries.death1: Oh, Reverend Oni`antae, how I have failed you! Save me from despair!
entries.death2: May the Reverend Oni`antae sacrifice you to the Heart of Dathomir!
entries.death3: May the Heart of Dathomir flail the skin off your bones!
entries.death4: Infidel! You shall not escape the Reverend Oni`antae!
entries.death5: The Dark Veil Order shall avenge my death!
